sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent
    participant Client as MCP Client (Claude Code / Cursor)
    participant Keen as keen-mcp (JSON-RPC stdio)
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant API as Atlassian API

    Agent->>Client: tool call request
    Client->>Keen: JSON-RPC over stdio

    alt Read path (fast, local)
        Keen->>DB: local read
        DB-->>Keen: cached data
    else Write path (create, update)
        Keen->>API: REST request
        API-->>Keen: response
        Keen->>DB: update cache
    end

    Keen-->>Client: tool result
    Client-->>Agent: structured data
